{"tid":1660472,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"雪莉驟逝「IU停工神隱3天」　韓媒曝：她一直守在靈堂","createTime":"2019-10-17T13:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T16:27:56.000Z","uid":54733,"like":255,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"54a3e570901fea542b5e41798f1d673192008cdc","tid":1660472,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:52:49.000Z","msg":"娛樂中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n南韓女星雪莉（Sulli）14日被經紀人發現在家中身亡，得年僅25歲，消息傳出後震驚各界，其中IU在2年內陸續送走鐘鉉、雪莉兩位好友，加上事發後一直未有消息傳出，讓外界相當擔心她的狀態，不過有韓媒爆料，其實IU這3天一直在靈堂守著雪莉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/10/15/2185285-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F10%2F15%2F2185285-XXL.jpg&h=cf927e94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲IU跟雪莉是南韓演藝圈出了名的好姊妹。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雪莉驟然逝世，除了f(x)成員放下手邊工作送她最後一程外，許多韓星也取消行程或是發文表示哀悼，而據韓媒報導，雪莉靈堂設置好後，包括f(x)成員及許多好友都低調現身，和雪莉情同姊妹的IU這3天來更是一直待在靈堂陪伴雪莉，溫柔地送好友走完最後一程。<br />\n<br />\nIU與雪莉2011年因主持音樂節目《人氣歌謠》而結識，年紀相仿的兩人一拍即合，好感情也沒因辭去主持棒而消逝，在對方推出作品時會互相應援，私下互動也相當頻繁，雪莉就曾多次在社群平台透露IU為她煮飯並大讚好友的廚藝，日前還友情演出IU主演的韓劇《德魯納酒店》，多年來始終堅定的好感情羨煞不少粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n雪莉驟逝的消息傳出後，IU在2012年為她譜寫的歌曲《桃子》時隔7年重回音源榜，而IU即將推出的迷你5輯「Love poem」也由經紀公司宣布所有專輯預告日程全數暫停，由於IU和2年前驟逝的SHINee成員鐘鉉也是好友，短時間內送走2個摯友，粉絲們都相當擔心IU的狀況，紛紛湧入IG留言關心，希望她能堅強面對。（劉秀敏報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/e/news.aspx?newsid=620025\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fe%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D620025&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaASvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=e15c5dd0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fe%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D620025&h=eabbabd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/e/news.aspx?newsid=620025</a>"},{"pid":"1afba8e37c2eab280ff608ccfb4462fba0a80026","tid":1660472,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:53:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwJzHzo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwJzHzo.jpg&h=eb217258&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"7733744b1575111599ab4df9bcfbbbbc303d9bd8","tid":1660472,"uid":37146,"like":42,"dislike":352,"score":-310,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:10:47.000Z","msg":"IU真係邪，邊個同佢fd親都出事"},{"pid":"e662a8ed67d4b43e7a271679f0d317370cf424a4","tid":1660472,"uid":240608,"like":17,"dislike":213,"score":-196,"quote":{"pid":"7733744b1575111599ab4df9bcfbbbbc303d9bd8","tid":1660472,"uid":37146,"like":42,"dislike":352,"score":-310,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:10:47.000Z","msg":"IU真係邪，邊個同佢fd親都出事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:17:39.000Z","msg":"銀赫 幾時死？"},{"pid":"e4cd4280b083ee299451da4430534e6bd5a9cf54","tid":1660472,"uid":40272,"like":78,"dislike":218,"score":-140,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:19:17.000Z","msg":"iu呢個機心爆炸女人關公技巧真高"},{"pid":"c67dc48b13955652d95eb1d2820431d929407197","tid":1660472,"uid":276402,"like":14,"dislike":92,"score":-78,"quote":{"pid":"e662a8ed67d4b43e7a271679f0d317370cf424a4","tid":1660472,"uid":240608,"like":17,"dislike":213,"score":-196,"quote":{"pid":"7733744b1575111599ab4df9bcfbbbbc303d9bd8","tid":1660472,"uid":37146,"like":42,"dislike":352,"score":-310,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:10:47.000Z","msg":"IU真係邪，邊個同佢fd親都出事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:17:39.000Z","msg":"銀赫 幾時死？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:20:26.000Z","msg":"銀赫係屌佢啫 有話同佢fd咩"},{"pid":"f73651ac8d618696739c83c4e1bfad0b3603d322","tid":1660472,"uid":43061,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:38:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />滿月社長"},{"pid":"d5412ba100ba05e416c8ec8b64e8b407978b8c44","tid":1660472,"uid":56701,"like":78,"dislike":9,"score":69,"quote":{"pid":"7733744b1575111599ab4df9bcfbbbbc303d9bd8","tid":1660472,"uid":37146,"like":42,"dislike":352,"score":-310,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:10:47.000Z","msg":"IU真係邪，邊個同佢fd親都出事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T